import React from "react" import Exercise from "./Exercise" import NavBar from "./NavBar" import axios from "axios" function HomePage() { const handleExerciseButtonClick = (exerciseType) => { // Make a network request to the backend with exerciseType axios .get(`http://localhost:3000/api/exerciseTemplate?exerciseType=${exerciseType}`) .then((response) => { console.log(response.data); // Check the response data in the browser console }) .catch((error) => { console.error("Error fetching data from the server:", error); }); }; return (
handleExerciseButtonClick("loops")} />
) } export default HomePage
